1
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:07,933
The donor registry still cannot
find a match for Jasmine.

2
00:00:08,067 --> 00:00:10,133
I keep waiting for a miracle

3
00:00:10,267 --> 00:00:12,533
while my child's time
keeps running out.

4
00:00:12,667 --> 00:00:17,133
Aunt Marj, Uncle Paolo,
I will donate for Jasmine.

5
00:00:17,267 --> 00:00:18,567
Does your father know
about this?

6
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:21,400
- Dad already agreed.
- Where is Ashley?

7
00:00:21,533 --> 00:00:23,000
She is in her room.

8
00:00:23,133 --> 00:00:24,467
I just came from there.
She is not there.

9
00:00:25,367 --> 00:00:26,767
Paolo, what happened?

10
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:28,467
I thought you already talked
to Edward.

11
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:29,967
I thought everything was okay.

12
00:00:30,100 --> 00:00:31,367
But what choice do we have?

13
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:35,100
We have no right to overstep
Ashley's parents.

14
00:00:35,267 --> 00:00:37,633
She had my consent
as her biological parent

15
00:00:37,767 --> 00:00:40,233
- and I also have the right...
- You have a lot of nerve!

16
00:00:40,367 --> 00:00:41,900
What right
are you talking about?

17
00:00:42,033 --> 00:00:45,200
You threw away that right
the moment you gave her up.

18
00:00:45,333 --> 00:00:55,300
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

19
00:01:35,167 --> 00:01:36,267
Marj.

20
00:01:37,533 --> 00:01:38,833
Marj.

21
00:01:38,967 --> 00:01:40,967
[SPEAKS IN VISAYAN LANGUAGE]

22
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:43,767
God will take care of it.

23
00:01:48,433 --> 00:01:51,233
[SPEAKS IN VISAYAN LANGUAGE]

24
00:01:51,367 --> 00:01:57,400
But I keep waiting for a miracle
while my child's time runs out.

25
00:01:59,767 --> 00:02:00,700
But...

26
00:02:00,833 --> 00:02:03,300
They signed a consent form,
right?

27
00:02:03,433 --> 00:02:05,167
Can't you use that anymore?

28
00:02:06,333 --> 00:02:09,267
<i>Edward and I have varying views
on what is best for Ashley.</i>

29
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,700
<i>And as a mother,
I need to decide.</i>

30
00:02:11,833 --> 00:02:21,800
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

31
00:02:27,933 --> 00:02:29,667
This consent is useless now

32
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:33,200
because Edward and Thea already
refused.

33
00:02:33,333 --> 00:02:43,300
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

34
00:02:45,267 --> 00:02:48,967
The donor registry still cannot
find a match for Jasmine.

35
00:02:52,433 --> 00:02:55,300
[SOBBING]

36
00:02:55,433 --> 00:02:57,867
What kind of mother am I?

37
00:03:00,167 --> 00:03:03,167
For Jasmine, we will do
everything to save her.

38
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:06,533
But everything we do
feels useless.

39
00:03:07,667 --> 00:03:09,133
Marj, do not say that.

40
00:03:10,233 --> 00:03:12,200
We are doing everything we can.

41
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:16,800
Until the end,
no matter what happens,

42
00:03:16,933 --> 00:03:18,633
we will not give up.

43
00:03:27,133 --> 00:03:28,733
Aunt Marj!

44
00:03:29,833 --> 00:03:31,267
Uncle Paolo!

45
00:03:33,233 --> 00:03:35,933
- Ashley!
- Who are you with here?

46
00:03:36,067 --> 00:03:37,700
You are walking already?

47
00:03:37,833 --> 00:03:39,933
I thought you were injured.

48
00:03:40,067 --> 00:03:42,000
And what are you doing here?

49
00:03:42,133 --> 00:03:43,500
I am okay now.

50
00:03:43,633 --> 00:03:47,333
My injury last time
was not that serious.

51
00:03:47,467 --> 00:03:51,867
And Mommy already allowed me
to come here.

52
00:03:54,833 --> 00:03:58,500
Did they not forbid you
from visiting Jasmine?

53
00:03:59,633 --> 00:04:03,833
[TENSE MUSIC]

54
00:04:03,967 --> 00:04:06,533
Mom could not sleep.

55
00:04:06,667 --> 00:04:08,267
She feels guilty.

56
00:04:10,033 --> 00:04:12,000
She told me she could not live
with herself

57
00:04:12,133 --> 00:04:14,233
if something happened
to Jasmine.

58
00:04:14,367 --> 00:04:16,467
Because of her stubbornness.

59
00:04:19,033 --> 00:04:21,833
Wait. Are you saying that...

60
00:04:21,967 --> 00:04:24,067
Yes, Uncle.

61
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,733
Mom already agreed.

62
00:04:27,733 --> 00:04:30,233
I will donate for Jasmine.

63
00:04:30,367 --> 00:04:39,867
[TENSE MUSIC]

64
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,633
Ashley, you have no idea
how much you made us happy

65
00:04:41,767 --> 00:04:43,767
with what you said.

66
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:45,967
Marj...

67
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,567
our prayers have been answered.

68
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:53,433
Aunt Marj, are you not happy?

69
00:04:53,567 --> 00:04:57,167
It is not that, Ashley.

70
00:04:57,300 --> 00:05:00,267
I thought...

71
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,800
they did not want to.

72
00:05:02,967 --> 00:05:06,767
I was just surprised
your mother agreed.

73
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:10,167
Last time I've talk to them,
they are very much against it.

74
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:12,367
Does your father know
about this?

75
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,233
Yes, Aunt.

76
00:05:16,367 --> 00:05:19,000
They already had a serious talk.

77
00:05:19,133 --> 00:05:23,967
Mom explained it to Dad. That is
why he also agreed.

78
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:28,033
If that is the case,
why are they not with you?

79
00:05:31,633 --> 00:05:36,533
Mom is still recovering
from the car accident last time.

80
00:05:38,367 --> 00:05:41,233
And Dad will follow later.

81
00:05:41,367 --> 00:05:42,533
They made me go first.

82
00:05:42,667 --> 00:05:46,567
They know Jasmine needs
the donor.

83
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:48,733
The situation is urgent.

84
00:05:51,367 --> 00:05:53,700
Paolo, can you call Edward?

85
00:05:55,033 --> 00:05:57,433
If he's really okay with this.

86
00:05:57,567 --> 00:05:59,600
I just want to be sure.

87
00:06:00,833 --> 00:06:02,233
Okay.

88
00:06:07,033 --> 00:06:08,300
I'll just call him.

89
00:06:08,467 --> 00:06:10,733
Mrs. Torrecampo,
can I talk to you for a minute?

90
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,133
Uncle Paolo...

91
00:06:18,267 --> 00:06:22,700
Uncle Paolo, please do not.
Please do not call Dad.

92
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:27,267
- Why, Ashley?
- I lied to you.

93
00:06:28,367 --> 00:06:30,133
What?

94
00:06:30,267 --> 00:06:32,133
Ashley, this is wrong.

95
00:06:32,267 --> 00:06:33,867
We cannot do this
without their consent.

96
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,533
I know, Uncle.

97
00:06:35,667 --> 00:06:37,533
I know this is wrong.

98
00:06:37,667 --> 00:06:41,033
But it doesn't matter anymore if
this is right or wrong.

99
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:44,067
But Jasmine's life is at stake.

100
00:06:47,033 --> 00:06:49,000
I love Jasmine.

101
00:06:49,833 --> 00:06:53,033
Especially now,
that I know that we're siblings.

102
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:56,667
I cannot bear to lose her.

103
00:06:56,800 --> 00:07:00,600
And I haven't done anything
to try and save her.

104
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:06,400
So please, just allow me.

105
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,567
Just let me donate.

106
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:13,267
For Jasmine's recovery.

107
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:17,133
If you do not allow me now...

108
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:21,467
Jasmine might die.

109
00:07:23,967 --> 00:07:25,600
Is that what you want?

110
00:07:25,733 --> 00:07:29,667
For your daughter to die because
you're scared of my parents?

111
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:39,767
[INTENSE MUSIC]

112
00:07:54,533 --> 00:07:58,033
Did you talk to them?

113
00:07:58,167 --> 00:08:00,167
Are they really okay with it?

114
00:08:03,367 --> 00:08:05,567
Yes, love.
I already spoke to them.

115
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:07,433
They already gave
their blessing.

116
00:08:09,367 --> 00:08:12,867
[SOBBING]
I thought they wouldn't agree.

117
00:08:15,900 --> 00:08:19,800
Doctor,
here is Ashley's consent.

118
00:08:19,933 --> 00:08:21,400
It is from her mother.

119
00:08:21,567 --> 00:08:31,533
[INTENSE MUSIC]

120
00:08:33,467 --> 00:08:34,900
Oh, I see.

121
00:08:36,933 --> 00:08:39,167
Since Ashley is still a minor,

122
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:42,967
I still need to verify the
physical presence of her parent

123
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:46,467
or legal guardian before
we proceed with the procedure.

124
00:08:49,167 --> 00:08:50,600
Doctor...

125
00:08:53,767 --> 00:08:57,867
Doc, I am the biological father
of Ashley.

126
00:08:58,033 --> 00:09:03,100
And Edward, his father,
is also on the way.

127
00:09:04,433 --> 00:09:07,900
Doc,
we are unning out of time.

128
00:09:09,367 --> 00:09:11,700
Jasmine needs this.

129
00:09:13,300 --> 00:09:18,667
She might get weaker with every
minute that passes by.

130
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:23,133
Let us start he procedure.

131
00:09:23,267 --> 00:09:25,533
My child's life
is on the line.

132
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:28,000
Please.

133
00:09:29,700 --> 00:09:30,900
All right.

134
00:09:31,033 --> 00:09:34,300
We'll start the initial workups
and preparation immediately.

135
00:09:35,733 --> 00:09:37,933
Ashley, follow me please.

136
00:09:38,067 --> 00:09:48,033
[INTENSE MUSIC]

137
00:10:02,733 --> 00:10:04,400
Ash?

138
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:07,367
Thea?

139
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:10,367
Ashley.

140
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:17,567
Thea!

141
00:10:18,833 --> 00:10:20,500
Where's Ashley?

142
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:26,200
- She's in her room.
- I checked, she's not there.

143
00:10:27,767 --> 00:10:30,133
Before I went shopping,
she said she'll take a nap.

144
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,533
I told you,
don't leave her alone.

145
00:10:35,567 --> 00:10:37,267
Ashley!

146
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,733
Ash!

147
00:10:40,967 --> 00:10:42,333
Ashley!

148
00:10:43,933 --> 00:10:45,800
Where could she have gone?

149
00:10:45,933 --> 00:10:51,567
[INTENSE MUSIC]

150
00:10:51,700 --> 00:10:53,367
Oh my gosh.

151
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:56,767
Ashley's just pretending
that she's still hurt.

152
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:00,967
Where could she have gone?

153
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:05,033
There is only one place
she would go.

154
00:11:05,167 --> 00:11:10,733
[INTENSE MUSIC]

155
00:11:18,767 --> 00:11:20,800
You have no shame!

156
00:11:20,933 --> 00:11:24,000
You probably guilt-tripped
my child into agreeing.

157
00:11:24,133 --> 00:11:26,133
Bring my child out!
Where is she?

158
00:11:26,267 --> 00:11:29,233
Thea, wait!
What are you talking about?

159
00:11:29,367 --> 00:11:31,400
I thought you already agreed.

160
00:11:31,533 --> 00:11:33,433
I thought you already explained
it to Edward,

161
00:11:33,567 --> 00:11:35,533
that is why you gave
Ashley your blessing here.

162
00:11:35,667 --> 00:11:36,800
Marj, what agreement?

163
00:11:36,933 --> 00:11:39,100
We will not risk
Ashley's safety!

164
00:11:39,233 --> 00:11:40,800
Our decision has not changed.

165
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:44,967
Paolo, what happened?

166
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,833
What?

167
00:11:46,967 --> 00:11:48,533
I thought you already talked
to Edward.

168
00:11:48,667 --> 00:11:50,833
I thought everything
was settled.

169
00:11:50,967 --> 00:11:53,033
I am sorry, Marj.
I was desperate.

170
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:57,067
I do not want my child to die,
so I lied.

171
00:11:57,200 --> 00:12:00,633
[INTENSE MUSIC]

172
00:12:00,767 --> 00:12:02,033
What?

173
00:12:06,467 --> 00:12:09,200
Do not pretend to be innocent,
Marj.

174
00:12:10,233 --> 00:12:13,533
I know you were the one
desperate for Ashley to donate.

175
00:12:13,667 --> 00:12:17,033
Thea, if I only knew,
I would not agree.

176
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:20,200
Then bring her out. Right now!
We are taking her home.

177
00:12:20,333 --> 00:12:21,333
- Where is she?
- Where is my child?

178
00:12:21,467 --> 00:12:24,267
Edward, it is too late.
Ashley is already inside.

179
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:26,000
The procedure
is already ongoing.

180
00:12:26,133 --> 00:12:29,400
[GASPS] You animal!

181
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:33,567
- You animal!
- Thea, listen first!

182
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:37,267
You animal! What?

183
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:41,067
You will not stop
until you get what you want?

184
00:12:42,167 --> 00:12:45,967
You will even use my child
for your own interests?

185
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:46,933
Thea, listen first.

186
00:12:47,067 --> 00:12:49,400
I do not care
about your explanation.

187
00:12:51,367 --> 00:12:55,967
If anything bad happens
to my child, I will kill you.

188
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:57,667
You animal!

189
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,767
[CLAMORING]

190
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:02,200
- How could you do this to me?
- Enough, Thea! Enough!

191
00:13:02,333 --> 00:13:03,000
[CLAMORING]

192
00:13:03,133 --> 00:13:04,200
Enough!

193
00:13:04,333 --> 00:13:06,367
[CLAMORING]

194
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,800
Enough!

195
00:13:07,933 --> 00:13:10,933
- Enough!
- [CLAMORING]

196
00:13:11,067 --> 00:13:11,867
- Thea, listen to me!
- Enough!

197
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,967
You have the nerve to fight me.

198
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:16,767
- [CLAMORING]
- Stop!

199
00:13:19,067 --> 00:13:20,600
Enough!

200
00:13:23,067 --> 00:13:24,367
Let go of me!

201
00:13:30,133 --> 00:13:35,200
If something happens to my
child, you will pay, Marj!

202
00:13:35,333 --> 00:13:37,700
Believe me.

203
00:13:37,833 --> 00:13:39,800
You and your spouse!

204
00:13:41,767 --> 00:13:46,133
And I do not care even if
your blood runs in Ashley.

205
00:13:46,267 --> 00:13:48,233
I will have you jailed.

206
00:13:48,367 --> 00:13:49,433
Enough!

207
00:13:49,567 --> 00:13:58,733
[INTENSE MUSIC]

208
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,500
My child! Ashley!

209
00:14:00,633 --> 00:14:02,067
Ashley!

210
00:14:03,233 --> 00:14:05,600
Ashley!

211
00:14:05,733 --> 00:14:07,733
[SOBBING]

212
00:14:07,867 --> 00:14:08,833
What is this?

213
00:14:08,967 --> 00:14:18,933
[INTENSE MUSIC]

214
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:26,533
What will your apology do now?
It already happened.

215
00:14:26,667 --> 00:14:28,000
You disobeyed us.

216
00:14:28,167 --> 00:14:30,633
You and Jasmin's parents acted
ahead of us.

217
00:14:31,433 --> 00:14:32,633
What?

218
00:14:32,767 --> 00:14:35,200
Can they put back
what they took from your body?

219
00:14:37,667 --> 00:14:40,533
Aunt Marj did nothing wrong.

220
00:14:41,867 --> 00:14:43,533
I was the one who lied to her.

221
00:14:43,667 --> 00:14:46,067
But Paolo still allowed it.

222
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:49,367
My child,
I understand you want to help.

223
00:14:50,367 --> 00:14:53,233
But what if something
happens to you?

224
00:14:53,367 --> 00:14:56,800
Jasmine received help.
Will she be able to help you?

225
00:14:56,933 --> 00:14:58,267
Thea, quit it.

226
00:15:02,933 --> 00:15:04,333
Your anger will not change
anything.

227
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:07,300
What happened
already happened.

228
00:15:11,733 --> 00:15:13,400
Let Ashley rest first.

229
00:15:14,667 --> 00:15:16,800
You can see she is weak.

230
00:15:16,933 --> 00:15:20,967
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

231
00:15:21,100 --> 00:15:23,300
To be honest,

232
00:15:23,433 --> 00:15:26,167
if this happened again,

233
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:28,700
I would still do it for Jasmine.

234
00:15:31,733 --> 00:15:33,233
I want her to survive.

235
00:15:33,367 --> 00:15:39,133
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

236
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:41,000
I know, my child.

237
00:15:44,167 --> 00:15:47,367
I know you are both disappointed
in me.

238
00:15:49,533 --> 00:15:53,233
But I will not apologize
for helping her.

239
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:58,667
But I ask for forgiveness.

240
00:15:58,800 --> 00:16:01,300
Because I did not obey you.

241
00:16:03,100 --> 00:16:04,367
I am sorry.

242
00:16:05,533 --> 00:16:08,833
Please forgive me, Dad...

243
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,167
Mom.

244
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:22,267
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

245
00:16:31,933 --> 00:16:35,067
Paolo, you should not have lied.

246
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,767
And what?

247
00:16:36,900 --> 00:16:40,633
Would you stop her if you
knew Thea never truly agreed?

248
00:16:42,167 --> 00:16:46,133
Marj, I am not saying
what we did was right.

249
00:16:46,267 --> 00:16:47,967
But what choice do we have?

250
00:16:48,100 --> 00:16:50,200
Our child's life is at stake.

251
00:16:50,333 --> 00:16:54,100
We have no right to overrule
Ashley's parents.

252
00:16:56,567 --> 00:16:58,633
Okay, I am sorry about that.

253
00:16:59,667 --> 00:17:02,500
Look, what is
done is done.

254
00:17:03,533 --> 00:17:07,533
What matters is that
Jasmine's procedure succeeds.

255
00:17:08,867 --> 00:17:12,233
Then we will deal with the rest.

256
00:17:14,033 --> 00:17:16,233
What if Ashley gets hurt?

257
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:19,133
What if Thea carries out
the threat?

258
00:17:19,267 --> 00:17:21,733
What if they file a case
against you?

259
00:17:21,867 --> 00:17:24,733
I will not let
that happen.

260
00:17:24,867 --> 00:17:27,300
No matter what they do.

261
00:17:27,433 --> 00:17:30,133
I will not let that happen.

262
00:17:30,267 --> 00:17:31,633
Especially to you.

263
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:35,300
Because you did
nothing wrong.

264
00:17:37,100 --> 00:17:40,867
And I will not let them
take us away from Jasmine.

265
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:45,200
Then humble yourself.

266
00:17:45,333 --> 00:17:47,767
Admit you were wrong to Edward.

267
00:17:49,133 --> 00:17:51,100
Do everything
so they forgive you.

268
00:17:51,233 --> 00:18:01,200
[INTENSE MUSIC]

269
00:18:15,433 --> 00:18:25,400
[PENSIVE MUSIC]

270
00:18:28,033 --> 00:18:29,267
What are you doing here?

271
00:18:33,733 --> 00:18:35,633
I just wanted to check
on Ashley.

272
00:18:35,767 --> 00:18:38,600
How is she? Is she okay?

273
00:18:38,733 --> 00:18:41,633
If she is not okay,
you will know.

274
00:18:44,167 --> 00:18:47,600
I just wanted to thank Ashley
for what she did for Jasmine.

275
00:18:49,333 --> 00:18:52,667
I will tell her.
You should leave now.

276
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:54,067
Bro, I am sorry.

277
00:18:55,500 --> 00:18:57,900
I am sorry
because I allowed Ashley

278
00:18:58,033 --> 00:19:00,167
to lie to both you and Thea.

279
00:19:00,300 --> 00:19:03,967
Paolo,
you did not just allow it.

280
00:19:04,100 --> 00:19:05,633
You disregarded her safety.

281
00:19:05,767 --> 00:19:07,767
You put her life at risk.

282
00:19:09,867 --> 00:19:11,533
Please, let me just talk to her.

283
00:19:11,667 --> 00:19:12,800
You cannot.

284
00:19:13,967 --> 00:19:16,900
You know, technically,

285
00:19:17,033 --> 00:19:20,367
I could sue you. You and Marj.

286
00:19:23,367 --> 00:19:24,633
Wait,

287
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:28,933
is that why you are here,
apologizing to me,

288
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:30,100
because you are afraid

289
00:19:30,233 --> 00:19:33,200
that Thea and I will push
through with suing you?

290
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:35,167
No.

291
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:38,300
I am here to apologize since
that is the right thing to do.

292
00:19:38,433 --> 00:19:39,467
The right thing

293
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:42,067
is that you should not gamble
with Ashley's life.

294
00:19:43,533 --> 00:19:46,767
Leave now
while I am still holding back.

295
00:19:50,333 --> 00:19:51,900
Ashley gave consent.

296
00:19:52,033 --> 00:19:57,633
[INTENSE MUSIC]

297
00:19:57,767 --> 00:20:00,733
She had my consent
as her biological father.

298
00:20:00,867 --> 00:20:03,333
- And I also have the right...
- You have a lot of nerve!

299
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:05,433
What right are
you talking about?

300
00:20:05,567 --> 00:20:08,867
You threw away that right
the moment you gave her up.

301
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:11,500
As long as my name is on
Ashley's birth certificate,

302
00:20:11,633 --> 00:20:14,767
you have no right over her
in any way.

303
00:20:17,467 --> 00:20:20,933
As long as my blood runs
through her veins,

304
00:20:21,067 --> 00:20:23,100
I have rights over her.

305
00:20:25,367 --> 00:20:26,700
And admit it.

306
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:32,067
If something does happen to her,
you are going to need my help.

307
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:34,567
Because you still
need my money.

308
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:36,667
You do not get it, Paolo.

309
00:20:36,833 --> 00:20:38,500
This is karma.

310
00:20:38,633 --> 00:20:40,600
Your karma is that your child
might die

311
00:20:40,733 --> 00:20:44,133
because you are greedy,
deceitful, and arrogant.

312
00:20:44,267 --> 00:20:54,233
[INTENSE MUSIC]

313
00:20:58,933 --> 00:21:01,467
Take that back!

314
00:21:01,600 --> 00:21:03,633
- Take that back!
- Oh my god!

315
00:21:03,767 --> 00:21:04,700
Edward!

316
00:21:04,833 --> 00:21:05,933
Paolo!

317
00:21:06,067 --> 00:21:07,300
Take it back!

318
00:21:07,433 --> 00:21:09,000
Stop this!
What is wrong with you?

319
00:21:11,467 --> 00:21:14,333
You are being so loud!
You will disturb Ashley!

320
00:21:14,467 --> 00:21:16,267
Leave now!

321
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,967
- Leave now!
- Enough!

322
00:21:18,100 --> 00:21:28,067
[INTENSE MUSIC]

323
00:21:40,233 --> 00:21:43,133
Be thankful that is all you got
from Edward!

324
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:49,367
I did not even get to talk
to Ashley.

325
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:54,333
I was not even able to ask
how she is doing.

326
00:21:54,467 --> 00:21:56,233
Edward is right.

327
00:21:56,367 --> 00:21:58,900
You have no right to talk
to your child.

328
00:22:04,133 --> 00:22:06,233
Are you accepting
that Ashley is my child?

329
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:13,867
Whether I accept it or not,
I cannot change the truth.

330
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:18,233
And besides,
Ashley has grown close to me.

331
00:22:19,467 --> 00:22:21,467
That is probably why...

332
00:22:23,067 --> 00:22:24,733
it came easily to me.

333
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:27,733
Marj.

334
00:22:29,467 --> 00:22:31,967
Mr. and Mrs. Torrecampo.

335
00:22:32,100 --> 00:22:34,800
Jasmine's procedure is finished.

336
00:22:34,933 --> 00:22:36,933
How is she?

337
00:22:37,067 --> 00:22:38,567
Is your child okay?

338
00:22:38,700 --> 00:22:42,033
[INTENSE MUSIC]

339
00:22:42,533 --> 00:22:43,133
It is still too early to tell.

340
00:22:43,267 --> 00:22:44,633
All we can do now is wait

341
00:22:44,767 --> 00:22:48,200
to make sure Jasmine's body will
accept

342
00:22:48,333 --> 00:22:50,667
the stem cells from Ashley.

343
00:22:50,833 --> 00:22:52,000
I will step out for now.

344
00:22:52,133 --> 00:22:57,667
[HEAVY MUSIC]

345
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:59,000
She is going to be okay.

346
00:23:00,733 --> 00:23:01,867
I hope so.

347
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:11,967
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

348
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:33,367
[LIGHT MUSIC]

349
00:23:34,367 --> 00:23:36,267
Xander?

350
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:38,000
How are you feeling?

351
00:23:38,133 --> 00:23:40,400
What are you doing here?

352
00:23:40,533 --> 00:23:41,967
Did you forget?

353
00:23:43,733 --> 00:23:47,600
Didn't you tell me about
going through your transplant?

354
00:23:47,733 --> 00:23:49,233
Oh, right.

355
00:23:49,367 --> 00:23:53,167
I wanted to make sure that you
are okay after the procedure.

356
00:23:53,300 --> 00:23:54,733
Does it hurt?

357
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:58,033
Hey, hey, just relax.

358
00:23:58,167 --> 00:24:00,567
- I am okay.
- Just relax.

359
00:24:02,067 --> 00:24:06,833
I am still a bit tired even
though I was just lying there.

360
00:24:06,967 --> 00:24:10,267
It felt like my strength
was literally drained.

361
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:12,100
You know that feeling?

362
00:24:12,233 --> 00:24:17,100
Imagine donating and going
through emergency surgery

363
00:24:17,233 --> 00:24:18,967
to save someone else's life.

364
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:22,367
Selfless.

365
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:24,133
You are heroic, Ashley.

366
00:24:25,700 --> 00:24:27,767
You are exaggerating
with heroic.

367
00:24:29,867 --> 00:24:31,533
That is why I like you
even more.

368
00:24:31,667 --> 00:24:33,067
What do you mean?

369
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,433
Once you get better,

370
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:37,667
once you leave this place,

371
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:40,433
I will formally talk
to your parents.

372
00:24:40,567 --> 00:24:42,900
For what?

373
00:24:43,033 --> 00:24:45,500
I will court you, Ashley.

374
00:24:45,633 --> 00:24:46,600
What?

375
00:24:46,733 --> 00:24:49,400
I am not as heroic as you,

376
00:24:49,533 --> 00:24:52,300
but I am going to strive
to do everything

377
00:24:53,667 --> 00:24:55,633
to be worthy of your yes.

378
00:24:55,767 --> 00:25:05,733
[LIGHT MUSIC]

379
00:25:10,733 --> 00:25:16,433
[LIGHT MUSIC]

380
00:25:16,567 --> 00:25:19,900
Your color is improving, my
child, and you are eating again.

381
00:25:22,033 --> 00:25:23,933
I do feel a lot better, Mom.

382
00:25:24,067 --> 00:25:27,400
It feels like I am less tired,
not like before.

383
00:25:29,133 --> 00:25:31,767
- That's good. Here.
- Well, there's a reason for it.

384
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:35,467
The doctor said the engraftment
was successful.

385
00:25:35,633 --> 00:25:36,800
Really?

386
00:25:36,933 --> 00:25:39,033
Jasmine's condition
is very promising.

387
00:25:39,167 --> 00:25:42,633
So after a few more days
of observation, you can go home.

388
00:25:42,767 --> 00:25:44,133
Soon.

389
00:25:44,267 --> 00:25:46,267
Mommy, I am going
to get better.

390
00:25:48,333 --> 00:25:52,633
[LIGHT MUSIC]

391
00:25:52,767 --> 00:26:02,733
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

392
00:26:08,133 --> 00:26:09,833
How is your child, Edward?

393
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:12,200
She's still in the hospital,
under observation.

394
00:26:12,333 --> 00:26:15,233
In case there are side effects
from the bone marrow harvesting.

395
00:26:15,367 --> 00:26:17,000
This is because of Paolo.

396
00:26:17,133 --> 00:26:19,800
It was not enough for him
that he humiliated me.

397
00:26:19,933 --> 00:26:21,967
He even put my child's life
in danger.

398
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:23,700
Do you want revenge on him?

399
00:26:23,833 --> 00:26:24,767
You know, Greg,

400
00:26:24,900 --> 00:26:27,033
did you not think
that because of how you act,

401
00:26:27,167 --> 00:26:29,333
Edward holds resentment
toward you?

402
00:26:29,467 --> 00:26:31,767
I should have disowned that boy
a long time ago.

403
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:35,533
You never showed
even a little love for him.

404
00:26:35,667 --> 00:26:36,767
How can I love him?

405
00:26:36,900 --> 00:26:39,200
Every time I look at you,

406
00:26:39,333 --> 00:26:42,367
all I can think about
is what you did to me.

407
00:26:44,433 --> 00:26:46,833
Marj, this is your fault.

408
00:26:46,967 --> 00:26:49,933
This is your fault
for what happened to my child.

409
00:26:50,067 --> 00:26:53,300
My child is convulsing
and I cannot do anything.

410
00:26:53,433 --> 00:26:56,267
Edward is right.
The heavens are punishing me.

411
00:26:56,400 --> 00:27:00,167
While Jasmine is getting better,
this is happening to Ashley.

412
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:03,200
If you want to prove
that you are a decent parent,

413
00:27:03,333 --> 00:27:05,733
make sure Marj pays.

414
00:27:07,233 --> 00:27:09,367
You will regret
what you did to me.
